_header: Felix was I-bore in Rome sometime by old daw
_description: Life of Pope Felix III, in one MS of the South English Legendary — in couplets

Bod779.First Lines:
Felix was I bore in rome sumtyme be olde dawehis fader heet felix
                    ek a man of þe olde lawe…
Bod779.Last Lines:
…Now bidde we god & seint felix þat he vs grace
                    sendeþat we after oure ending day mot to heuene wende
